modName: Nouser Face and body tattoo for RaceMenu
summary: Face and body tattoos for RaceMenu used in my various race.
descriptionHtml:
Just a stand alone upload of the face tattoo/paint and body paint textures for my races. Supports most face, and the body ones have some for both CBBE and UNP.
You need [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] (Or similar) to make use of them.
You can use in your own mod if you wish, tell me first though.

And a note for browsing, anything with M next to it is for male. Unlabeled is either female or unisex.

Used my races, as obvious by the plugin names.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/8464]Kaleen Race[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36871]Khartor Race[/url]
author: Nouser
